701145f-a.title: Bronx: Grand Concourse - 158th Street (East)
701145f-a.text:
Grand Concourse (left), west side, south from East 16lst to East
158th Street,showing the Bronx County Court House. 2n the right is the
East 161st street side of the court house, extending west to Walton Ave.
Also shown is the north end of Frans Sigel Park at East 158th Street.
1933.
Wurtr Brothers.

701144f-a.title: Bronx: Grand Concourse - 158th Street (East)
701144f-a.text:
Grand Concourse (Mott Ave.), at the S.E. corner of East 158th Street,
showing the Fleischmann Laboratories. The view is southeastward across
East 158th Street.
May 16, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.
